OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to take Jersey
OL,4,CMinister to court
OL,6,FBrittany Ferries has taken the
OL,7,FMinister responsible for Jersey's
OL,8,Fferry tender process to Jersey's Royal
OL,9,FCourt.
OL,11,FBretagne Angleterre Ireland S.A.
OL,12,F(Brittany Ferries) is taking legal
OL,13,Faction against Deputy Kirsten Morel in
OL,14,Fhis capacity as Sustainable Economic
OL,15,FDevelopment Minister.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday 24 December, the Royal
OL,18,FCourt ruled that Brittany Ferries had
OL,19,Fmet the legal threshold to take the
OL,20,FMinister to court over his conduct
OL,21,Fduring the ferry tender process.
