OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to take Jersey
OL,4,CMinister to court
OL,6,FJersey's government has called
OL,7,FBrittany Ferries' decision to take
OL,8,Flegal action "disappointing" but added
OL,9,Fthey "respect the Court process".
OL,11,FThey add: "Unless any Court process
OL,12,Fbeforehand prevents it, the contract
OL,13,Fwith DFDS will come into effect at
OL,14,Fjust after 5pm on 31 December 2024."
OL,16,FDFDS' Chris Parker says: "We expect
OL,17,Fthe contract between DFDS and the
OL,18,FGovernment of Jersey to come into
OL,19,Fforce on December 31st."
