OL,6,FThe judicial review won't apply to the
OL,7,Fdecision to exit the joint procurement
OL,8,Fprocess with Guernsey and reject both
OL,9,FDFDS and Condor.
OL,11,FHowever, it relates to the decision
OL,12,Fmade in the Jersey-only process - and
OL,13,Fonly on the grounds of bias and
OL,14,Funfairness.
