OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to take Jersey
OL,4,CMinister to court
OL,6,F"Brittany Ferries was given leave to
OL,7,Fchallenge the decision of the Minister
OL,8,Freached on 3 December 2024, by
OL,9,Freference to allegations of procedural
OL,10,Funfairness and apparent bias limited
OL,11,Fto the matters set out in this
OL,12,Fjudgment."
OL,14,FThe Commissioner adds: "I appreciate
OL,15,Fthat this decision may have
OL,16,Fsignificant ramifications for the
OL,17,FGovernment of Jersey and its desire to
OL,18,Fenter into a contract with DFDS.
