OL,4,CMinister to court
OL,6,F"However, that is not a relevant
OL,7,Fconsideration in relation to whether
OL,8,For not to grant leave if the relevant
OL,9,Ftest is met and a trial is required.
OL,11,F"Rather, it is relevant to the Court
OL,12,Fand the parties making every effort to
OL,13,Fhave matters resolved as soon as
OL,14,Fpossible so that all parties and, more
OL,15,Fgenerally, the island know where they
OL,16,Fstand."
