OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to take Jersey
OL,4,CMinister to court
OL,6,FIn an internal email sent to Condor
OL,7,FStaff on Monday 23 December, Brittany
OL,8,FFerries CEO Christophe Mathieu said:
OL,9,F"We feel very strongly that we should
OL,10,Fstand up for what is right and for
OL,11,Fwhat all of our staff deserve, after
OL,12,Fmany years of dedicated (sic) service
OL,13,Fto the Islands.
OL,15,F"Last Friday (20 December), I attended
OL,16,Fthe Royal Court in Jersey to challenge
OL,17,Fthe government's decision to appoint
OL,18,FDFDS.
OL,26,@tD@YpmtD@]pn
