OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F385A1735479571
OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to take Jersey
OL,4,CMinister to court
OL,6,F"Our priority has always been to
OL,7,Fensure that the Channel Islands have
OL,8,Fthe best possible ferry services, and
OL,9,Fthe procurement process showed DFDS
OL,10,Fare best placed to deliver those
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,F"We conducted a full and fair
OL,14,Fprocurement process. The marking and
OL,15,Fevaluation were independently
OL,16,Foverseen, and DFDS won the bid by a
OL,17,Flarge and clear margin.
OL,19,F"Jersey needs high-quality, good
OL,20,Fvalue, and resilient sea connectivity,
OL,21,Fand we are determined to deliver it.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
