OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to take Jersey
OL,4,CMinister to court
OL,6,F"We are working hard with DFDS to
OL,7,Ffinalise the details of ferry services
OL,8,Ffor next year, and it is already clear
OL,9,Fthat they will be better than the
OL,10,FIsland currently enjoys.
OL,12,F"The last thing Islanders need is more
OL,13,Funcertainty over ferry services, and
OL,14,Fwe hope Britanny Ferries will respect
OL,15,Fthat.
OL,17,F"We are grateful to Condor for the
OL,18,Fservice it has provided for Islanders
OL,19,Fover the years and we would prefer the
OL,20,Frelationship not to end on this note.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
