OL,3,CBrittany Ferries to take Jersey
OL,4,CMinister to court
OL,6,F"At a hearing on 20 December, the
OL,7,FRoyal Court gave Brittany Ferries
OL,8,Fpermission to challenge only a limited
OL,9,Faspect of our decision-making process
OL,10,Fby a judicial review. All their other
OL,11,Fgrounds were rejected.
OL,13,F"There will be a further hearing
OL,14,Fbefore the Royal Court on 13 and 14
OL,15,FJanuary 2025 to decide the limited
OL,16,Fground of challenge."
